# It seems that I encountered an error while trying to harvest iron ore, indicating that there was "Nothing within reach to harvest." This could mean that I am not positioned correctly relative to the iron ore or that the patch is depleted.
#
# To resolve this, I should first check if there are any nearby iron ore patches that I can harvest from. 

# Let's find the nearest iron ore patch again to ensure I am targeting the correct location.
nearest_iron_ore_position = nearest(Resource.IronOre)

# Moving to the nearest iron ore patch.
move_to(nearest_iron_ore_position)  # Move to the nearest iron ore patch.
